# this ignore, DocAgent's own scanner indexes those clones as if they
# were part of DocAgent's source tree, and `api_reference` produces
# `docs/reference/benchmarks.regeneration.clones.<repo>.*.md` files with
# broken cross-links (each file links to siblings that may not exist).
